    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028290/extras/7df4fc3a74a3f33fc605df4eacc9303c.poster.avif?t=1723083188\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028290/extras/7df4fc3a74a3f33fc605df4eacc9303c.webm?t=1723083188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028290/extras/7df4fc3a74a3f33fc605df4eacc9303c.mp4?t=1723083188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>操地狱</strong>是一款无情的俯视视角动作射击游戏，将玩家推向宇宙解放者的角色。在这款残酷且快速的游戏中，你将与感染无限太空的恶魔害虫战斗。装备广泛的武器库，你将粉碎头骨，摧毁他们的胜利希望，并将恐惧植入敌人的黑暗灵魂中。每场在宇宙飞船上的战斗都是一场生存斗争，敌人会掉落弹药等宝贵资源和其他关键补给。游戏无情的战斗和无限的战场确保了充满肾上腺素的体验，让你保持在座椅的边缘。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028290/extras/9d8c55e4c0e6d44a070f558f0a80a5b7.poster.avif?t=1723083188\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028290/extras/9d8c55e4c0e6d44a070f558f0a80a5b7.webm?t=1723083188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028290/extras/9d8c55e4c0e6d44a070f558f0a80a5b7.mp4?t=1723083188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈战斗:</h2></strong> 参与高强度的战斗，对抗恶魔害虫，利用多种武器消灭敌人。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >资源管理:</h2></strong> 从击败的敌人那里收集弹药和其他重要资源，以维持你的进攻和生存。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >俯视视角:</h2></strong> 享受对混乱战场的清晰视野，允许战略移动和精确瞄准。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽战斗:</h2></strong> 在无限的太空环境中体验无情的战斗，确保持续的动作和挑战。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >氛围设计:</h2></strong> 沉浸在黑暗、地狱般的太空氛围中，通过详细的图形和音效增强体验。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li></ul>",
